import React, { useState } from 'react'; import './CreateAppointment.css'; import { useAppointments } from './AppointmentsContext'; function CreateAppointment() { const [patientName, setPatientName] = useState(''); const [testType, setTestType] = useState(''); const [radType, setRadType] = useState(''); // New state for Rad type const [urgency, setUrgency] = useState(''); // New state for Urgency const { addAppointment } = useAppointments(); const handleSubmit = async (e) => { e.preventDefault(); const appointmentData = { patient_name: patientName, test_type: testType, rad_type: radType, urgency: urgency, }; await addAppointment(appointmentData); // Now awaiting the async operation // Reset form fields here if needed }; return (
setPatientName(e.target.value)} placeholder="Nombre del paciente" /> setTestType(e.target.value)} placeholder="Observaciones" /> {/* Rad Type Dropdown */} {/* Urgency Dropdown */}
); } export default CreateAppointment;
